Class MusicXml2MsmMpmConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.musicxml.MusicXml2MsmMpmConverter

  • public class MusicXml2MsmMpmConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class does the conversion from MusicXML to MSM and MPM To use it, instantiate it with the constructor, then invoke convert().
